OL,3,CParents 'heartbroken' over proposed
OL,4,Cclosure of Bradbury House
OL,6,FParents whose children attend a
OL,7,Frespite centre in Liverpool say they
OL,8,Fare "heartbroken" at its proposed
OL,9,Fclosure.
OL,11,FBradbury House at the Royal School for
OL,12,Fthe Blind in Wavertree provides
OL,13,Fresidential stays for children with
OL,14,Fcomplex needs.
OL,16,FBut from next Summer, the school says
OL,17,Fit will no longer offer respite stays
OL,18,Fbecause of funding pressures.
