OL,3,CParents 'heartbroken' over proposed
OL,4,Cclosure of Bradbury House
OL,6,FThe proposed closure comes just weeks
OL,7,Fafter children's hospice Zoe's Place
OL,8,Fwas saved.
OL,10,FSeveral mums have said they are
OL,11,Fdevastated and their children have
OL,12,Fnowhere else to go, including Alison
OL,13,FMooney and her son Alex, who has
OL,14,Fcerebral palsy.
OL,16,FAlison said: "It is genuinely
OL,17,Fheartbreaking. It's been a home away
OL,18,Ffrom home for Alex when he has needed
OL,19,Fit the most."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
