OL,3,CParents 'heartbroken' over proposed
OL,4,Cclosure of Bradbury House
OL,6,FShe continued: "It's bee a respite for
OL,7,Fall of us, not just for Alex. It's
OL,8,Flovely for him going there to see his
OL,9,Ffriends and the fact that it will be
OL,10,Ftaken away from us is really
OL,11,Fupsetting."
OL,13,FJulia Clarke's son Anthony has used
OL,14,FZoe's Place and Bradbury House, but
OL,15,Fnow they're faced with nowhere to go.
