OL,3,CParents 'heartbroken' over proposed
OL,4,Cclosure of Bradbury House
OL,6,FJulia said: "I really feel sick. I
OL,7,Fknow there is no other place that
OL,8,FAnthony can go. His needs are too
OL,9,Fcomplex for other respite's so that's
OL,10,Fthe grey area where there's lack of
OL,11,Ffacility for them children and it's so
OL,12,Funfair."
OL,14,FStacey's son Benjamin is registered
OL,15,Fblind and has severe learning
OL,16,Fdisabilities. She and the other
OL,17,Fparents have started a campaign to
OL,18,Fkeep Bradbury House open.
