OL,3,CParents 'heartbroken' over proposed
OL,4,Cclosure of Bradbury House
OL,6,FStacey said: "Bradbury helps all of us
OL,7,Fas a family. It's not just for
OL,8,FBenjamin, it's not just for me. It's
OL,9,Ffor all of us.
OL,11,F"At least when he is at B, I can have
OL,12,Fthat break and that rest. But equally
OL,13,Fit's a break from him because he gets
OL,14,Findependence away from mummy."
OL,16,FShe continued: "It is frustrating and
OL,17,Fit should have never got to this point
OL,18,Fat all in the first place. But at the
OL,19,Fend of the day, when it comes to our
OL,20,Fchildren, we are their advocate."
